      • toJSONString

        public java.lang.String toJSONString()
        Description copied from class: GenericValue
        Writes the field value into a json payload. This method is critical in the code paths that involve inserting or updating Entry objects. This is the code that correctly inserts each field value into the JSON.

        Note, the compound field types must override this method to write their unique structures into the json (file, image, location).
